text: Deep End is a 1970 British German psychological drama movie directed by Jerzy Skolimowski and starring Jane Asher, John Moulder-Brown, Karl Michael Vogler, Chris Sandford, Diana Dors, Burt Kwouk, Erica Beer, Cheryl Hall.
